      "name": "Speech Recording",
      "abstract": "Speech recording connects audio quality, speaker context, prompts, transcripts, metadata and review workflows into a durable voice record.",
      "description": "Speech recording is the directed capture of spoken language with enough technical, contextual and consent metadata to support review, reuse and preservation.",
